ondary-font\">Anime Episode(s)</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Episode_22\" title=\"Episode 22\">Episode 22</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<table class=\"pi-horizontal-group pi-horizontal-group-no-labels\">\n\t<caption class=\"pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-secondary-background pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Guide</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"previous\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_44\" title=\"Chapter 44\">Chapter 44</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"next\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_46\" title=\"Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n<nav class=\"pi-navigation pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background pi-secondary-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Chapter_45_Images\" title=\"Category:Chapter 45 Images\">Chapter 45 Images</a></nav>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Trial by Hashira</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\"><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">鬼</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>き</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">殺</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>さい</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">隊</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>たい</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">柱</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>ちゅう</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">合</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>ごう</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">裁</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>さい</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">判</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>ばん</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby></span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Kisaitaichū gō saiban</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Installing Japanese character sets\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#198975;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is the forty-fifth chapter of <a href=\"/wiki/Koyoharu_Got%C5%8Dge\" title=\"Koyoharu Gotōge\">Koyoharu Gotōge's</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" title=\"Kimetsu no Yaiba (Manga)\">Kimetsu no Yaiba</a>.\n<p></p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Summary\">Summary</span></h2>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 182px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/7/76/Shinobu%27s_introduction.png/revision/latest?cb=20200207174002\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Shinobu's_introduction.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Shinobu%27s_introduction.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Shinobu explains that Tanjiro is being put on trial.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro</a> wakes up confused on the ground before the <a href=\"/wiki/Hashira\" title=\"Hashira\">Hashira</a> after being knocked unconscious. <a href=\"/wiki/Shinobu_Kocho\" title=\"Shinobu Kocho\">Shinobu</a> is the first to speak and informs Tanjiro that he has arrived at the Demon Slayer Headquarters and is being put on trial. The scene cuts to inform the viewer with more background information regarding the Hashira. The Hashira are the highest ranked swordsmen among the Demon Slayers. They have mastered different forms of breathing techniques that general Demon Slayers have not, and are the ones sustaining the Demon Slayer Corps.\n</p><p>The scene returns back to the main storyline introducing each Hashira and their perspectives of the trial. The Flame Hashira is introduced as <a href=\"/wiki/Kyojuro_Rengoku\" title=\"Kyojuro Rengoku\">Kyojuro Rengoku</a>, who comments that a trial would not be necessary since Tanjiro violated the conduct, mentioning that the only plausible option would be to decapitate Nezuko. The next swordsman introduced is the Sound Hashira, a tall muscular man with a unique, painted accent around his left eye, who goes by the name <a href=\"/wiki/Tengen_Uzui\" title=\"Tengen Uzui\">Tengen Uzui</a>. The third member thats introduced is the Love Hashira, <a href=\"/wiki/Mitsuri_Kanroji\" title=\"Mitsuri Kanroji\">Mitsuri Kanroji</a>, who felt sorry about possibly having to kill a cute girl. The fourth member thats introduced is the Stone Hashira, <a href=\"/wiki/Gyomei_Himejima\" title=\"Gyomei Himejima\">Gyomei Himejima</a>, who appears to be crying while praying. The fifth member can be seen staring aimlessly at the clouds, and is introduced as the Mist Hashira, <a href=\"/wiki/Muichiro_Tokito\" title=\"Muichiro Tokito\">Muichiro Tokito</a>. \n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tright show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 182px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/a/a0/Obanai%27s_introduction.png/revision/latest?cb=20200207173414\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Obanai's_introduction.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"166\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\"></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/a/a0/Obanai%27s_introduction.png/revision/latest?cb=20200207173414\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/a/a0/Obanai%27s_introduction.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/180?cb=20200207173414\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"166\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"Obanai&#39;s introduction.png\" data-image-key=\"Obanai&#39;s_introduction.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/a/a0/Obanai%27s_introduction.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/180?cb=20200207173414\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Obanai%27s_introduction.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">The Serpent Hashira, Obanai Iguro, questions Giyu's intentions.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>With the majority of the Hashira agreeing to decapitate Nezuko, Tanjiro is left rattled and desperately looks around for his sister. However, his train of thought is suddenly cut off when he hears a voice coming from above. He looks up to see a young man loitering in the tree above, who is introduced as the Serpent Hashira, <a href=\"/wiki/Obanai_Iguro\" title=\"Obanai Iguro\">Obanai Iguro</a>. Obanai points at <a href=\"/wiki/Giyu_Tomioka\" title=\"Giyu Tomioka\">Giyu Tomioka</a> and demands to know what his punishment will be for violating the Demon Slayer conduct. Shinobu mentions that they can think of Giyu’s punishment after they hear Tanjiro's reasoning for protecting a Demon.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 182px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/2/2c/Sanemi_profile_pic.png/revision/latest?cb=20170203224342\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Sanemi_profile_pic.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"205\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\"></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/2/2c/Sanemi_profile_pic.png/revision/latest?cb=20170203224342\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/2/2c/Sanemi_profile_pic.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/180?cb=20170203224342\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"205\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"Sanemi profile pic.png\" data-image-key=\"Sanemi_profile_pic.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/2/2c/Sanemi_profile_pic.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/180?cb=20170203224342\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Sanemi_profile_pic.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">The Wind Hashira grabs hold of Nezuko.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>Tanjiro begins to explain his reasons for travelling with a Demon, however the pain from his injuries prove to be to great for him to ignore. Shinobu approaches him and gives Tanjiro some water laced with painkillers to ease his pain. After drinking some water given to him, Tanjiro proceeds to explain that his sister was turned into a Demon, but has never eaten someone before, vowing that she would never hurt a living person. Despite his pleas, Obanai and Gyomei do not sympathize with his reasoning and Tanjiro continues to try to appeal to them.\n</p><p>Not long after this, the last Hashira arrives holding <a href=\"/wiki/Nezuko_Kamado\" title=\"Nezuko Kamado\">Nezuko’s</a> box. A swordsman with white hair and covered in scars is introduced as the Wind Hashira, <a href=\"/wiki/Sanemi_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Sanemi Shinazugawa\">Sanemi Shinazugawa</a>. He mocks Tanjiro for carrying a Demon around with him and proceeds to draw his blade before stabbing the box. Enraged, Tanjiro charges at Sanemi and manages to headbutt him. However, before they could continue the fight, the leader of the Demon Slayers arrives to begin the trial.&nbsp;\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></h2>\n<div style=\"width:auto; height:200px; overflow:auto; margin-bottom:3px; padding-left:0.5em; border:.5px solid #AARRGGBB; -moz-border-radius-topleft:0.5em; -webkit-border-top-left-radius:0.5em; border-top-left-radius:0.5em;\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro Kamado</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tengen_Uzui\" title=\"Tengen Uzui\">Tengen Uzui</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Mitsuri_Kanroji\" title=\"Mitsuri Kanroji\">Mitsuri Kanroji</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Kyojuro_Rengoku\" title=\"Kyojuro Rengoku\">Kyojuro Rengoku</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Muichiro_Tokito\" title=\"Muichiro Tokito\">Muichiro Tokito</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Gyomei_Himejima\" title=\"Gyomei Himejima\">Gyomei Himejima</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Shinobu_Kocho\" title=\"Shinobu Kocho\">Shinobu Kocho</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanemi_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Sanemi Shinazugawa\">Sanemi Shinazugawa</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Giyu_Tomioka\" title=\"Giyu Tomioka\">Giyu Tomioka</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Obanai_Iguro\" title=\"Obanai Iguro\">Obanai Iguro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nezuko_Kamado\" title=\"Nezuko Kamado\">Nezuko Kamado</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Kagaya_Ubuyashiki\" title=\"Kagaya Ubuyashiki\">Kagaya Ubuyashiki</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span></h2>\n<ul><li>The Hashira are formally introduced.</li>\n<li>Tanjiro has a scuffle with the Wind Hashira, Sanemi Shinazugawa.</li></ul>\n\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20210108112331\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.189 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.212 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 9338/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 169881/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 78727/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 28/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  123.793      1 -total\n 74.81%   92.605      1 Template:Manga_Navigation\n 71.61%   88.647      1 Template:Navibox\n 43.72%   54.125     26 Template:Navibox/info\n 37.61%   46.554     26 Template:Element_List\n 18.68%   23.119      1 Template:Chapter_Infobox\n 11.79%   14.598     26 Template:Force_Font_Color\n  3.58%    4.431      1 Template:Nihongo\n  2.73%    3.383      1 Template:Infobox/Scroll_Box\n  1.54%    1.909      7 Template:Ruby\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key prod:kimetsunoyaiba:pcache:idhash:348-0!canonical and timestamp 20210108112331 and revision id 75633\n -->\n</div>"}